SUMMARY="Rust libary that targets the creation of Amstrad CPC demos"
DESCRIPTION="cpclib is a library that aims at helping to develop Amstrad CPC demos. Maybe it \
could be usefull for other z80 platform or even games. None of the functionalities are 100% \
functional. I have only implemented the subset I need for my current Amstrad CPC demo project. \
Several tools are provided in addition to library."
HOMEPAGE="https://github.com/cpcsdk/rust.cpclib/"
COPYRIGHT="2026 Romain Giot"
LICENSE="MIT"
REVISION="1"
